{"type": "article", "id": 9173, "title": "Midwest Vintage & Woaw 牛仔拼布系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-05T06:48:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235310NxV41Do7RFzwIalH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t香港最著名的美式复古服饰专卖 Midwest Vintage 与潮流生活店 Woaw 联手推出了一个牛仔拼布系列，包括 T 恤，无袖夹克、短裤、钮扣衬衫等男女装服饰，以及电脑包，围裙等生活方式单品。他们从美国西部服饰汲取灵感，使用拼接面料，将丹宁元素融入设计之中。目前该系列计划在 5 月 7 日至 28 日于 WOAW Store “WOAWWEST” 主题 Pop-up 期间限定店铺发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353065xjaImGVMkKluRPo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235306xwOLai6X4Qe5yV7H.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235307UnDwrQMlOdANqSmg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235307rKdvAgPc8aF1342o.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235307ScZvtMLNxB1WTQrA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235308hf1X6gnMpwHqRbIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353080Zo53FdDtT2OBazx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235309JvGlHdUqKDsa2ifE.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235309BUDp9NJymihwA60c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235310C